OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781830076
OL,3,CMum of Cape Verde goalkeeper Vozinha
OL,4,Cgranted visa to watch him at World Cup
OL,6,FThe mum of Cape Verde goalkeeper
OL,7,FVozinha is expected to attend his next
OL,8,FWorld Cup match after the US granted
OL,9,Fher a visa to travel.
OL,11,FJosimar Dias, 40, became a global
OL,12,Fsensation during Cape Verde's 0-0 game
OL,13,Fagainst Spain on Monday, saving seven
OL,14,Fgoals in what was his team's first-
OL,15,Fever World Cup match.
OL,17,FBut speaking after the game, Vozinha
OL,18,Fsaid his mother had not been able to
OL,19,Fattend because of the $15,000 (around
OL,20,F#11,000) bond payment Cape Verdeans
OL,21,Fmust pay to get a US visa.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
