OL,3,CMum of Cape Verde goalkeeper Vozinha
OL,4,Cgranted visa to watch him at World Cup
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"She didn't manage to be here because
OL,12,Fof the visa ... the money we have to
OL,13,Fpay for the visa. We didn't manage on
OL,14,Ftime, and I would like her to be
OL,15,Fhere," he told reporters.
OL,17,FA source familiar with the matter told
OL,18,FITV News' US partner CNN that they
OL,19,Funderstood Vozinha's mother also does
OL,20,Fnot have a passport, but is in the
OL,21,Fprocess of obtaining one.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
