OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781830076
OL,3,CMum of Cape Verde goalkeeper Vozinha
OL,4,Cgranted visa to watch him at World Cup
OL,6,FShe is expected to make it to Miami in
OL,7,Ftime for Cape Verde's next game
OL,8,Fagainst Uruguay on Sunday, after the
OL,9,FUS State Department and House Minority
OL,10,FLeader Hakeem Jeffries intervened.
OL,12,F"Cape Verdeans in America and
OL,13,Fthroughout the diaspora have been
OL,14,Fcelebrating the underdog grit and
OL,15,Fresilience of the Blue Sharks, joined
OL,16,Fby soccer fans from nations throughout
OL,17,Fthe globe," Jeffries said in a
OL,18,Fstatement.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@KO]
