CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781830076
OL,3,CMum of Cape Verde goalkeeper Vozinha
OL,4,Cgranted visa to watch him at World Cup
OL,6,F"That joy was tempered a bit when
OL,7,FVozinha tearfully revealed that his
OL,8,Fown mother was unable to watch her
OL,9,Fson's iconic performance in person due
OL,10,Fto visa complications. No mother
OL,11,Fshould miss the chance to see her
OL,12,Fchild make history.
OL,14,F"Upon learning of this development, I
OL,15,Fspoke with Secretary of State Marco
OL,16,FRubio and asked the State Department
OL,17,Fto do everything in their power to
OL,18,Fensure that his mother can attend Cabo
OL,19,FVerde's next match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
