PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781830076
OL,3,CMum of Cape Verde goalkeeper Vozinha
OL,4,Cgranted visa to watch him at World Cup
OL,6,F"It is a privilege to announce that
OL,7,FVozinha's mom will be able to secure a
OL,8,Fvisa in time to attend their game this
OL,9,FSunday against Uruguay. All fees have
OL,10,Fbeen waived consistent with official
OL,11,Fpolicy.
OL,13,F"Travel arrangements are now being
OL,14,Fmade for mother and son to reunite in
OL,15,FMiami."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
