OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781830076
OL,3,CMum of Cape Verde goalkeeper Vozinha
OL,4,Cgranted visa to watch him at World Cup
OL,6,FCape Verde is one of 50 countries
OL,7,Fwhose citizens must pay a deposit of
OL,8,Fup to $15,000 to enter the US, which
OL,9,Fthe government says is due to high
OL,10,Fnumbers of nationals overstaying their
OL,11,Fvisas.
OL,13,FThe Trump administration exempted
OL,14,Ffootball fans from the requirement in
OL,15,FMay, providing they can prove they
OL,16,Fhave valid tickets to the World Cup.
OL,18,FA US official told CNN the bond had
OL,19,Falso been waived for the relatives of
OL,20,Fall World Cup players.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
