OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781830076
OL,3,CMum of Cape Verde goalkeeper Vozinha
OL,4,Cgranted visa to watch him at World Cup
OL,6,F"The US Department of State has no
OL,7,Frecord of this individual applying for
OL,8,Fa visa," they said in reference to
OL,9,FVozinha's mother.
OL,11,F"All relatives of players are eligible
OL,12,Ffor visa bond waivers, and the
OL,13,FDepartment is actively reaching out to
OL,14,Fthis player's family to assist with
OL,15,Fvisa services."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
