OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781830076
OL,3,CMum of Cape Verde goalkeeper Vozinha
OL,4,Cgranted visa to watch him at World Cup
OL,6,FVozinha's performance against Spain
OL,7,Fturned him into an overnight
OL,8,Fcelebrity, with his Instagram
OL,9,Ffollowers shooting up from 50,000 to
OL,10,Fmore than 13 million in less than four
OL,11,Fdays.
OL,13,FCape Verde, a small island nation off
OL,14,Fthe coast of West Africa with a
OL,15,Fpopulation of under 500,000, is ranked
OL,16,F67th in the World Cup, while Spain is
OL,17,Fthe second favourite.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
