PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781830076
OL,3,CMum of Cape Verde goalkeeper Vozinha
OL,4,Cgranted visa to watch him at World Cup
OL,6,FVozinha began his career in 2011
OL,7,Fplaying for clubs in Cape Verde before
OL,8,Fbeing signed to teams in Angola,
OL,9,FMoldova and Portugal, and has been a
OL,10,Fpart of the national team since 2012.
OL,12,FAt 40 years and 12 days old, he is the
OL,13,Foldest player to feature in a nation's
OL,14,Ffirst World Cup match and the ninth
OL,15,Foldest player to ever play in the
OL,16,Ftournament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
